00:40:37,451 --> 00:40:38,751
Sobre o Joe.

736
00:40:39,498 --> 00:40:40,898
Sobre o Wally.

737
00:40:41,592 --> 00:40:42,892
E a Iris!

738
00:40:44,035 --> 00:40:46,491
Sabe de nossos pontos fortes,
nossos medos.

